section.heading: Commission on Out of School Time Grants and Youth Outcomes; nongovernmental members' appointment, terms.

annotations.annotation: Applicability of D.C. Law 21-261: § 12 of D.C. Law 21-261 provided that the creation of this section by § 7 of D.C. Law 21-261 is subject to the inclusion of the law’s fiscal effect in an approved budget and financial plan. Therefore that amendment has not been given effect.
